accurately generate any physical user-specified static magnetic field in the\ninterior of a closed cylindrical shield of any length, enabling the development\nand miniaturization of systems that require accurate magnetic shielding and\ncontrol.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2020 16:13:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Jun 2020 13:59:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 8 Jun 2020 19:57:38 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 23 Jun 2020 16:42:13 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 7 Sep 2020 18:22:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-09"}
