atial resolution when compared with\ntraditional systems. These results enable the design of new prototypes for the\nmuography of natural and artificial structures of strategic interest. We are\ncurrently assembling a prototype detector that will use this methodology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2020 22:50:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Jun 2021 23:54:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-14"}
