otion recognition models\nand outperform the existing data augmentation methods such as conditional VAE,\nGaussian noise, and rotational data augmentation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2020 21:23:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2020 08:09:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-18"}
